                          <h3 class="heading-style-h5 is-font-size-landscape"><span class="text-color-primery">03. </span>Pack According to Orders</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-size-medium">Orders are packed to meet the specific needs of each customer, whether it’s a bulk delivery for a retailer or a single order for a school or club.</p>
